(125, 1, '2019-08-11 20:58:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We all know that <a href=\"https://diary-of-a-pothead.com/tobacco-is-evil/\">tobacco is evil</a>, and which pot smoker hasn\'t realised that removing tobacco from their lives would be a good thing? That\'s something I\'ve been thinking about for a long time. I hate the coughing, the dirtiness and the unhealthiness of smoking, but I do it because it\'s how I consume cannabis. I want to change that and one answer is vaping. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Vaping devices are not just being used for nicotine – they are also being used to vaporise THC, the chemical responsible for most of marijuana\'s mind-altering effects, often through cannabis-infused oils in place of e-liquids.</p><cite><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Beyond Nicotine: Vaping Marijuana (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.centeronaddiction.org/e-cigarettes/recreational-vaping/beyond-nicotine-vaping-marijuana\" target=\"_blank\">Beyond Nicotine: Vaping Marijuana</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The problem is.... where to get hold of THC E-Juice? I\'m going to call that <strong>goop</strong>. There are certainly places in the world where very high quality goop can be legally purchased and consumed, but I don\'t live in one of those.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The best option for me is to make it myself. It\'s taken me nearly 6 months to collect all the materials together to make the first version</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>I needed to collect</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>1/4 Ounce of weed</li><li>1 small bottle of 95% proof alcohol</li><li>A rice cooker</li><li>Rubber spatula</li><li>Muslin</li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The answer is Goop', '